29 June 2010Government will brief media on its assessment of the country's hosting of the 2010 FIFA World Cup.The briefing will take place as follows: Date: Wednesday, 30 June 2010 Time: 12:00 Venue: Gauteng International Media and Tour Centre, Nelson Mandela Square (Sandton)Members of the media wishing to attend are requested to forward their names to:David Masango Cell: 083 279 7520 E-mail: davidm@gcis.gov.zaFor media enquiries contact: Pheliswa Sebati Cell: 082 413 4609Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)